                <p>The Shadowblight Necromancer is an S-Tier Shadow damage-over-time build that excels at AoE clear and speedfarming. The core mechanic revolves around landing <strong>8 Shadow damage instances within 2 seconds</strong> to trigger the Shadowblight passive, dealing massive bonus damage based on your weapon damage and Shadow multipliers. You sacrifice all minions via Book of the Dead for the Stand Alone damage reduction bonus, making this a solo-caster playstyle that is deceptively tanky.</p>
