                    <p style="color: #a0a0a0; font-size: 0.85rem; margin-top: 8px;">Abyssal increases Shadow damage and provides damage reduction against Shadow-afflicted enemies. The Frailty board's Legendary node applies a damage debuff to cursed enemies, which stacks with Decrepify and Aspect of the Damned for triple-layered curse scaling.</p>
